09">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29954674/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Magnetic+Resonance+Imaging+%28MRI%29+Assessment+of+Residual+Breast+Cancer+After+Neoadjuvant+Chemotherapy%3A+Relevance+to+Tumor+Subtypes+and+MRI+Interpretation+Threshold&amp;author=Y+Kim&amp;author=SH+Sim&amp;author=B+Park&amp;publication_year=2018&amp;journal=Clin+Breast+Cancer&amp;pages=459-467&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.clbc.2018.05.009&amp;pmid=29954674">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">24.</div><div id="r24" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Didonato R, Shapiro N, Koenigsberg T, D’Alfonso T, Jaffer S, Fineberg S. Invasive mucinous carcinoma of the breast and response patterns after neoadjuvant chemotherapy (NAC). <em>Histopathology</em> 2018;72(6):965–973.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1111/his.13451">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29220097/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Invasive+mucinous+carcinoma+of+the+breast+and+response+patterns+after+neoadjuvant+chemotherapy+%28NAC%29&amp;author=R+Didonato&amp;author=N+Shapiro&amp;author=T+Koenigsberg&amp;author=T+D%E2%80%99Alfonso&amp;author=S+Jaffer&amp;author=S+Fineberg&amp;publication_year=2018&amp;journal=Histopathology&amp;pages=965-973&amp;doi=10.1111%2Fhis.13451&amp;pmid=29220097">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">25.</div><div id="r25" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Leddy R, Irshad A, Hewett L, et al. Effects of Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy on Benign Breast Lesions Compared to Cancers: Should an 